Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People say that when someone dies, they go to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:07.07,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人が死んだら 天国に行けるという
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:11.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 僕はそうは思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't think that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When someone dies, I think that person journeys into people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:16.43,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだ人間は きっと誰かの心へ旅立つのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:21.24,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思い出となって 生き続けるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They live on as a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:25.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,父と母がそうだったように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like how my mother and father currently live on in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:28.16,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らの心に宿るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:32.81,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けれど それもやがて消えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But memories eventually fade with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why people want to leave something behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.64,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 人は何かを残したいと願うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So others won't forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:42.81,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れてしまわないように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:42.63,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと映ってんのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is it recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The viewfinder is black...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.91,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ファインダー真っ黒だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.56,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we'll remember them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.22,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ 何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:18.86,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ きれいな手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her hands were so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:22.79,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ俺 どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, what did I do yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:33.40,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで 海君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:37.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっと 昨日は 高感度フィルムのテストをしようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out to test my new high-speed camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そろそろ起きないと遅刻しちゃうわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:47.00,警示标语-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本字幕由诸神字幕组制作，仅供交流学习，禁止用于商业用途\N更多中日双语字幕，请登录www：Kamigami：org
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:47.00,人员名单-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日听：秋水无痕 翻译：yaya 校对：小草爱吃梨 gin 时间轴：小青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.65,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kai! It's time for you to wake up! You'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海外出張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for three months, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:53.20,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ 三ヶ月だけなんだけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:55.94,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ どこに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bolivia. My company needs people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.85,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ボリビア 人手が足りないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:01.69,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 海君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん 行ってきていいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking forward to it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.47,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行きたいんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ 行っておいでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself, and summer break is just around the corner anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 自炊できるし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.46,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もうすぐ 夏休みだし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw wild parties in my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人になるからって羽目外しすぎちゃダメよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:21.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, mind your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.22,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それと お行儀悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do some shopping on the way home, but I'll be back before seven at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:32.38,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰りに買い物とかしてくるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,七時までには 帰るから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった 行ってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっちも行ってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Home alone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.69,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人暮らしか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This'd make a pretty picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん いいロケーション
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Red hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.42,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,赤い 髪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.67,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜ どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is everyone staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.19,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなに目立ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:18.19,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何か 間違ってるのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kai, where will you shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.22,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でさ ロケ場所は決まったの 海君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you scouting for a location yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 ロケハンに行ってたんじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You had your camera with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:31.48,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それ持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was just trying it out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 昨日はただフィルムのテストし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a movie idea in mind, Mr. Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.43,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画撮るんだろう 監督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just recording things I see. Nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,適当に取ってるだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ なんとなく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... I was gonna help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手伝ってやろうと思ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Tetsuro stars in it, all the girls would get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:46.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けどけど 哲郎君が映画に出たら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.34,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,女子たちぎゃあぎゃあ言いそうかも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about you, Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうかさ 美桜こそどうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.87,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 美桜主演で行かねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, how about filming Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, so we could shoot something like an idol promo video...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夏だし アイドルのイメージビデオっぽくさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.92,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No cost involved, and you don't need a script.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:04.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,金もかからず 脚本も要らない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're thinking about... imagining me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:09.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぎょ凝視されてる 想像されてる うわ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Men sure are carnal creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,男子の欲望出まくり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.58,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,冗談だって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:13.79,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かしたいね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something? Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かって 何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かんないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're high schoolers after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:30.20,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあそうだな 何せ 俺ら 高校生だし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.43,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夏だし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.48,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね 何かしなくちゃかも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We should do something during the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,へえ 何撮ってんのかと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you filmed with so much devotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.22,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああいうのがタイプなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ カメラ回ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The camera's still recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや だから そう言うんじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:10.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なるほど 確かに さっきの人 柑菜とは正反対のタイプだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty much the complete opposite of Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょ どういう意味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! {\i1}How {\i0}exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いろいろと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you {\i1}how {\i0}exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.30,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから どういう意味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, "In many ways."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.70,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから いろいろだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you be less specific? You're always...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:18.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何よ それ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:22.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大体あんた まあまあ 落ち着きなよ 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth was right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.79,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,当然ながら 僕は気づいてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:27.50,signs,,0,0,0,,{\org(900,146)\pos(632,148)\fax-0.08\fs50\blur0.8\c&H202423&\b1\frz22.27\frx12\fry348}Staff {\fax-0.15}room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.52,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遅れてすみません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to attend school here from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.76,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日から こちらの学校に転入させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Takatsuki Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.23,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月 イチカです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The drama we're all a part of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.86,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちのドラマは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The bell's already rung! Homeroom, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら ホームルームはじめるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.09,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すでに動き出していること
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Open your books.{*** dashite}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already being caught on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カメラが回り始めていること
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:49.03,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,22)\fs60\blur0.8\1a&H10&\fnEraserDust\c&HCEC4BA&}Takatsuki Ichika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the clubs you used to be in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.73,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前の学校で部活とかしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a transfer student halfway through is kind of unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.46,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな時期 転校とか 珍しいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the color of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,髪の色 きれいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,付き合ってるやつとか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Buzz off, you hungry beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほらほら 散りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.05,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,飢えた狼ども
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yamano?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.34,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何何だよ 山乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.61,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいだろ 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our classmate now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:03.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,クラスメートだし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get yourselves in line,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんたたち おとなしくしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'm gonna have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:09.26,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すごいことするわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You free this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日の昼何する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like, yesterday on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:14.03,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうそう 昨日のテレビさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamano Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.07,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 山乃檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.87,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ えっと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takatsuki Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.19,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,貴月 イチカです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something weird about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.62,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 何かおかしいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the beginning of a beautiful friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私たち いい友達になれそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.46,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Yamano...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.35,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,山乃さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬でいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Lemon. Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.94,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん じゃあ 檸檬 一つ聞いていい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.{nanikashira}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.54,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かしら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing a different uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.07,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜ 違う制服を着てるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't tell. Top secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,内緒 すげえ内緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.67,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっ そう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's a weird combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それにしても 何か 偏った組み合わせね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:58.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 何かおかしいかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have carbohydrates, a drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.62,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,炭水化物と水分 平均的な組み合わせじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you normally buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there maybe some regional specialty—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何か珍奇的な食べ物とか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:05.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなた 変わってるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ど どこが どんな風に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうところが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:13.26,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,名前は貴月イチカさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Takatsuki Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in Class 3-A as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.81,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日つけて 三年A組に転入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's 160 cm tall. Weight is 41 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.81,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,身長は１６０センチ 体重四十一キロ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Her measurements are 92-56-88.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,３サイズは上から ９２ ５８ ８８
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her shoe size is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,靴のサイズは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you getting this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.54,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうやって調べた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.66,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:35.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 三年に転入してきた 先輩のプロフィル
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,can you tell me some things  about the third-year girl who transferred here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.47,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,教えてもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... fine, Ishigaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.42,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.80,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,石垣君ったら ほかの人に言っちゃダメよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't spread it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how the story goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.30,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とまあ そんな感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that somehow against the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.37,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪じゃないか それ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.85,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,「ありがとう」は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.28,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.72,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どういたしまして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.35,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなところで何してんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tanigawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川 や もうめし食ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Ate lunch already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:02.56,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん ああ そういうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また隠し撮りでもするつもり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to stalk someone with your camera again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.05,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ あれはたまたま シャッターを押しただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've hit record by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.03,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウソ ホントだって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.11,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.58,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ もう 叩きたい 痛いんでんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wanna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You already are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lover's quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:19.04,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.00,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,痴話喧嘩だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tanigawa, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.42,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よし 決めた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it! I don't have any cute bikinis or stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.78,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 無理だから 可愛い水着とか持ってないしだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.28,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海 行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:33.72,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行くってどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is something wrong with my food...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:36.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねっ ねえ 私のご飯 どこが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.36,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.41,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すいません ちょっといいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, can I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.65,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい 哲郎 お前 何する気だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいから 任せとけって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.34,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 別に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっと 何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Takatsuki Ichika, right? The one who transferred today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:55.80,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 今日転入してきた貴月イチカ先輩ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm first-year Ishigaki Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.38,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は 一年の石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kirishima Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.47,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちは霧島海人です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We were thinking of making a movie with our friends in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:04.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,実は 俺たち 仲間中で自主映画撮ろうとしてて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought it'd be nice to have you in it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:08.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 先輩 よかったら 俺らの映画に出演してもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that all about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい 急に何言い出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.19,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you really want me in it,{no, no, i want to be in YOU}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.97,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 私でよかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜひ 協力させて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once something starts moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:26.72,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一度動き出したものは簡単には止まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's hard to bring it to rest again.{like my dick}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:31.30,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちなみに 私も参加するわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:33.60,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm third-year Yamano Lemon. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.35,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,三年の山乃檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よろしく 自分でも気づかないうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Third-year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.96,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 三年 年上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're older than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the camera had already begun to roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カメラは 回り始めていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.91,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(807,224)\blur0.6}Episode One
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.91,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,406)\blur0.6\fs70}You shouldn't do that{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to ask others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:47.54,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 言ってみるもんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.10,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(643,121)\blur0.65\fnAndy\c&H181C1C&\fs40}You can all relax \N\N\N\N\N\Nat the pool this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか オーケーしてくれるのは思わなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, even I was surprised that she accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika is so forthcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.02,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ先輩 気前よすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.55,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,むちゃくちゃだよ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.73,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思いだったら すぐ実行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Act on your impulses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my motto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.16,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺のポリシーね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.35,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 気分がいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The view is great here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.84,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,眺めも最高
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like an old lecher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オヤジ癖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you really making a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえねえ ホントに作るの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already told the third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:13.11,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩に宣言しちゃったしな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it gonna be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.12,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ど どんな内容にするのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just going to leave that to our tiny senior Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:21.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこらへんはちっちゃい檸檬先輩に任せればいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:21.78,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんせ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:25.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 映画の内容は私に任せて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just leave the script to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a book with scripts I wrote for Lucas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.76,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょうど ルーカスのために書いておいた本があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hollywood level?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハリウッド級
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just doodling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ってか 勝手に書いただけですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Tehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.38,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とか言ってたし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:36.86,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 私も参加する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:45.91,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も 裏方とかなら 手伝えるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. Maybe I can help out backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.02,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いやいや 美桜は出演しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you belong on film, Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな ダメダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何で いいじゃん ダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A movie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:55.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画 ね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:11:02.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,監督 演技指導 お願いして いい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you teach me how to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll start with the {\i1}ins and unders{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 手取り 腰取り
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean {\i1}ins and outs{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:07.71,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,足取りですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.91,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや はあああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.32,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何笑ってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや なんでも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.63,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ていうか 何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これよこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:19.25,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 何が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a hickey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それ キスマークじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:23.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よ 用意いい ってなんだこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's a hickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.41,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから キスマーク
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:32.46,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ 昨日撮影してたときにでも虫に刺されたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess some bug bit me while I was filming yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:35.51,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ったく そんなの身に覚えがないって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I don't remember anything, tho—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He... suddenly fell silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な なんか 沈黙してる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it come to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見 見に覚えが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it you "discovered"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.38,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おいおい どんなロケしてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.72,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違うって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The peasants demanded that their tax be lowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.02,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,農民による地租軽減
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The bourgeoisie demanded the freedom to associate with other classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:55.05,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,庶民なによる自由な言論集会の改正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Many demanded that the country open itself to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.52,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,他国との対等条約の締結要請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:58.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,元気そうで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}These three currents...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.10,日文上-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え これら三つの主張を掲げ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow when summer break starts, let's all meet up and talk about the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:09.84,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 明日の休みは皆で集まって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.11,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画製作の決起集会ね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.07,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩たちには 俺から連絡しとくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call the third-year girls myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See you all tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.30,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ お先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.07,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.48,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.79,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 私も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.38,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お 気をつけてな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:30.91,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれで意外と楽しみにしてんだぜ 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:33.74,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.85,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,余計なことしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this was a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.60,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.83,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま きっかけは多いほうがいいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The more chances there are, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,頑張んな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.98,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういう上から目線 なんかむかつくんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It kinda pisses me off when you look down on people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.84,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何浮かれてんだ 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:09.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 映画か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This movie thing is a bit unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.92,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it right. I must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで 間違ってないはずだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何してんっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.70,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人です 霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Kaito. Kirishima Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.60,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.75,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや あそこから見えたんで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fishing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で それ釣りですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そうなの 私 こういうのが趣味なの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I've always liked fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice to know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それはそれでいいんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この川 魚いませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no fish in this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:53.43,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ ありがとう 教えてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks for telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.46,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お役に立てて何よりです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.47,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 まだ この辺 よく分からなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm new here. I don't know a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.59,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とっても助かっちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:07.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの 釣りなら もう少し行くと 大きな川にぶつかるんで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you want to fish, there's a bigger river with fish not that far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.34,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこなら きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.11,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 俺はこれで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, if you'll excu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:16.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん 何でも その これからよろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll be seeing you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.11,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ はい こちらこそ よろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.24,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え 惜しいことしたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I waste my chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こうもうちょっと会話を繋げてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've stuck with her for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.60,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何と言うか こう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.83,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずばり言いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.64,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ先輩は一人でここへ引っ越してきたんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you moved here alone, Ichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.71,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すっごい どうして分かったの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.64,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その手にしている荷物を見れば分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious from the luggage you're carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.40,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,簡単なプロファイリングですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm something of an armchair detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I concluded you must be alone and looking for a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして 俺は更にこう推理しました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩は住む場所がなくて困っている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely right again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.84,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,またまたすごい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.32,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,下宿先と何かトラブルがあった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay where you thought you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.92,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ピンポン ピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you're at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.78,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,正直路頭に迷ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:03.79,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんな場所で釣りをしていたのが何よりの証拠です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you were trying to fish there proves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding, ding, once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.09,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,またまたピンポン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:11.84,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 俺んち来ませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.76,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イチカ先輩さえよければ だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure I could?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当にいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.09,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろんです ちなみに ここが僕の家です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, this is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.32,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 大きなお家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.19,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだばあちゃんの家なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my dead grandma's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so huge half of it can't be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.24,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大きすぎで 持て余すほどです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩一人増えても どうってことはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,素敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, if we live together, I could teach you this and that about how to act in movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:38.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それに 一緒にいれば 映画の演技指導もできますから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All the {\i1}ins and unders{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.64,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それこそ 手取り 腰取り
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you mean {\i1}ins and outs{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.54,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは足取りだと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,は そうでした
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, dream's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で これ 現実ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.02,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あはい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.66,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えと いつから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.40,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,結構前から
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:58.04,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really glad, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.50,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも すごく助かる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.08,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私 本当に困ってたから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:07.43,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの 何の話す
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ 来ませんか 俺んちって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Wanna stay at my place?" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこから聞いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where you tuned in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.77,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で ちょっと待ってください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just me talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.91,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先のは その 俺の妄想っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.33,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,独り言で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, my sister lives here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:22.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それに うちには姉さんがいるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いきなり 女の子を家に連れ込んだりしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she would say if I suddenly brought a girl home with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.82,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっとうしちゃうと思うし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.12,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 無理を言って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.55,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの 先輩 どこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.49,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この辺で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to pitch a tent somewhere.{i'll help you pitch that tent}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか 野宿のしやすそうな場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.10,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ もう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.70,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 七海さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.28,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あら 柑菜ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.87,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,珍しいですね こんな早くにこんな場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare to see you around here so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:02.64,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仕事は引き継ぎだけだったし 用意もあったから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing someone else's job, and I had to get ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,用意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:07.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう なのに こいつが急に機嫌悪くなっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But my bike decided to break down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right. Kanna, can you lend me a hand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:09.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ 柑菜ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかったら ちょっとお手伝ってくれないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.13,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.41,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その辺座っててください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put your luggage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.41,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 荷物は取りあえず こっちに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おもっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:22.77,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうやってここまで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravi—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:24.14,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ グラビ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gravi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:24.78,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,グラ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I gradually got used to it. There's a trick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぐらっとさせてね コツがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.12,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とりあえず 一晩だけですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just for one night, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here tonight, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.40,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今晩だけは 泊めますから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.59,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:43.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 男の子の部屋に入るの 初めてだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is my first time in a boy's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.93,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっ そうなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:47.78,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ こんなにのんびりしてられないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We shouldn't just bum around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.72,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,食事は後で持ってきますから じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you some food later— Well, actually, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister will come home around seven, so you should take a shower before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.49,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その前に姉さんが帰ってくるのが七時ぐらいだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.56,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今のうちに シャワーを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have your clothes in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.97,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,着替え この中ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.15,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ご ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.02,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何入れてるんですか あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so this is the shampoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:09.59,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっと こっちがシャンプーで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pajamas, pajamas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,パジャマ パジャマ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nanami likes negligees...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.26,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえちゃん ネグリジェ派だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This should do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.02,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とりあえず 着るものは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:26.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,着 着替え 洗濯機の上に置いときますから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I put some clothes for you on the washing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.80,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.85,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,開けなくていいです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.26,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ七時までには 結構あるな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some time until seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.86,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ったく 何って日だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, today is killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩と会って
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I met her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.18,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画作ることになって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm making a movie with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.03,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜか先輩が家にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now she's sleeping at my place for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to clean up my stuff for now and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.70,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく 俺も荷物を片付けて 着替えして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This needs fixing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか これも 片付けとかなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.66,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何だ ここって 虫に刺された
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this where the bug bit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:14.25,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何だ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, these clothes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.04,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 この服なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:19.90,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.63,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君 海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito! Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.49,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたの しっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.54,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The metabolism... of his cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.89,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは セルの代謝が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.91,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it works...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.95,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかった 機能してる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.26,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫だから ね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.27,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ホント助かったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.20,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうね 柑菜ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:16.57,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いえいえ でも 三ヶ月の転勤ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No sweat. But will you really be gone for three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Take care of Kai for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:20.21,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなの 柑菜ちゃん 海君のこと頼むわね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.01,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんなら 泊まりに来ちゃってもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.06,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:29.45,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん 柑菜ちゃんのこと 応援してるんだけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.31,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ど どういう意味ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.65,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あら とぼけちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I should see an optometrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.00,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おねえちゃん また 目が悪くなったみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:48.85,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかね 光に包まれながら 海君が女の人と抱き合ってる幻が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this illusion of Kai being held by some girl while they were surrounded by light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.35,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何ですか それ おかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.68,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:57.47,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ あの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.83,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:10.29,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な なななななな 何してんのおおおっ ハメを外しすぎっっ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.63,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの とりあえず 離れて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you may well realize, I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,当然ながら 僕は気づいていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dynamite!{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:19.88,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知っているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.39,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残っているのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:37.20,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(738,448)\fs80\blur0.5\c&H0B0B0B&}With her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:37.20,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,352)\blur0.45\c&H0B0B0B&}Episode Two
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These overflowing feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:03.99,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたには 溢れ出す思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:06.17,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知られたくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.66,日文字体-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらなくて
